snippet.title: Armored Lab Force VULVEHICLES English PV
snippet.description:
Raze the road less traveled with your [b]Vulvehicle[/b], the ultimate all-purpose armored combat machine!
Whether flying through the sky or burrowing deep underground, these gals stop at nothing to blast through terrain and enemies alike in this comical action STG!

Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1957590/
